\ip God…®n akam inigha izir gumazim Obadia dughiar Babilonia iza Jerusalem gas…®ghas…®ghizim…®n g…®n uan akam…®n gun m…®gei. Fom…®ra Idomia Israelian apanim gami, egha dughiar Babilonia iza Jerusalemia gas…®ghas…®ghizim…®n, Idomia bar akonge, egha Babilonian akuragha paza Israelia gami. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, Obadia kamagh…®n God…®n otivir akabar gun m…®g…®a ghaze, God bar paz…®v…®ra Idomia damigham. Kantri Idom ko, kantrin igharaziba Israelian apanim gamiziba, me bar ovegham.
\c 1
\ms1 Idomian gumazamiziba arazir kuram gamiz…®ma, God men arazir kuram ikara
\s1 Idomian arazir kuram bang…®n, God ivezir kuram me dan…®ngam
\p 
\v 1 \x - \xo 1:1-14 \xt Aisaia 34:5-17; 63:1-6; Jeremaia 49:7-22; Esekiel 25:12-14; 35:1-15; Amos 1:11-12; Malakai 1:2-5\x*Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Ekiam akar kaba isa Obadia gan…®ngi, God arazitam Idomia damuamin akaba.
\b
\q1 Ikiav…®ra Itir God akam inigha izir gumazir mam amadaz…®ma, a kantriba bar adar ghu.
\q2 Ez…® e an akam baregha g…®fa.
\q1 A kamagh…®n m…®g…®a ghaze,
\q2 вАЬIa uarira uarir ariragh, egh d…®kavigh e mang…® Idomia m…®sogham.вАЭ
\b
\q1 
\v 2 Ez…® Ekiam kamagh…®n Idomia m…®gei:
\q1 вАЬK…® ian gavgaviba abight…®,
\q2 kantrin igharazibar gavgaviba ian gavgavibagh afiragham.
\q1 Eght…® gumazamiziba bar ian aghuagh d…®bovir akabar ia m…®k…®m,
\q2 egh ak…®rim ragh ia gasaragham.
\q1 
\v 3 \x - \xo 1:3 \xt 2 Atriviba 14:7; Aisaia 14:13-15; Akar Mogomem 18:7\x*Ia uari fer n…®ghn…®zimra ia gifari.
\q2 Dag…®ar gavgavir ekiaba ian nguibar ekiam, d…®vazim…®n m…®n anev…®niz…®ma,
